data.description: Welcome to your dream homestead! Situated on a sprawling 18 acres this property is perfect for the outdoorsman or homesteader with all the modern amenities and updates. The 40x50 shop building was built in 2022. New HVAC inside in 2022 and the outside in 2019. New water well footer and pump in 2022. All plumbing in the home was updated to PEX pipe in 2018. New pool in 2022. New hot water heater in 2019. Primary bath was updated in 2020 and shower glass in 2023. Original hardwood floors throughout. One acre stocked pond. Large fenced garden with raised HDPE food safe beds and watering system with chicken coop and run around the perimeter. Yes, the chickens can stay! This property also offers a lime tree, avocado tree, two fig trees, Magnolia trees, a peach tree, producing banana trees, wild blackberries, wax myrtles that line the driveway, and three Crape Myrtles. Large deer and wildlife love to roam the property as well. Schedule your showing today.
